text: Highly recommended! Dr. Sam is a meticulous and thoughtful doctor. He is patient and provides accurate prognoses. The clinic's charges are reasonable, ensuring you receive excellent care. All the clinic staff is also very helpful and polite.

Took a medical health screen here. Had a consultation with Dr Samuel. Results came back quick with extensive details. Followed up with a thorough review. Very happy with the service at this clinic. Highly recommend!
Just visited this clinic today. All the staff at this clinic are very friendly and professional. Overall, very satisfied with the service and the comfortable atmosphere they provide.

I got pico laser treatment there for three times, my spots are getting lighter and lighter.  Dr. Lua is professional and patient to solve my skin problems, and nurses are very kind.  Highly recommend!

Dr Samuel is experienced and professional. I had my vaccination done here and it was fast and painless. It takes less than 5 mins to walk from Lavender mrt to the clinic which is very convenient. Highly recommend this clinic.
